=== 评价 ===
電影收穫了廣泛的好評<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/gravity-tracking-could-warner-bros-637408|title='Gravity' Tracking: Could Warner Bros. Space Epic Open to $40 Million?|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=September 26, 2013|accessdate=March 30, 2016|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414040209/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/gravity-tracking-could-warner-bros-637408|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影評人大多稱讚演員的表現、導演、攝影、視覺效果及3D的運用<ref>{{cite web|last=Trumbore|first=Dave|url=http://www.collider.com/gravity-reviews/|title='Gravity' Reviews Praise Sandra Bullock and George Clooney's Performances|publisher=Collider|date=August 28, 2013|accessdate=August 28, 2013|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301085454/http://collider.com/gravity-reviews/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的315篇專業影評文章，其中303篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為96%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]9分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gravity_2013/|title=''Gravity''|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=May 31, 2014|archive-date=2017-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171104143118/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gravity_2013/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的49篇評論文章，全數皆給出好評，平均分為96（滿分100），成為2014年第二高的廣泛發行電影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/gravity|title=''Gravity'' Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=September 19, 2013|archive-date=2014-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728005301/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/gravity|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[影院评分|CinemaScore]]於首映週末的調查，觀眾給予電影的平均評價於A+至F間落於「A-」<ref name="MSN">{{cite web|last=Cunninghham|first=Todd|title='Gravity' soars to record-breaking box-office blast-off|url=http://movies.msn.com/movies/article.aspx?news=831933|publisher=[[MSN_Entertainment|MSN Entertainment]]|accessdate=October 6, 2013|date=October 6, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006191146/http://movies.msn.com/movies/article.aspx?news=831933|archive-date=2013-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

